<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Smart Centre 16 months shr 67.6 cents.</title>
<headline>Smart Centre 16 months shr 67.6 cents.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>16 months ended June 30 vs 12 months ended February 28, 1995</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr, attrib (cts)     67.6	  vs 42.1</p>
<p>    Div (cts)		 16.0	  vs 12.5</p>
<p>    Attrib income	   28.91	 vs 16.04</p>
<p>    Pre-tax		   44.26	 vs 26.35</p>
<p>    Tax			 14.43	 vs 9.18</p>
<p>    Interest paid	   16.50	 vs 6.67</p>
<p>    Turnover		 469.02	 vs 272.25</p>
<p>Div payable October 16</p>
<p>on register September 13</p>
<p>Full name: Smart Centre Holdings Ltd</p>
<p>NOTE - The company said it would offer capitalisation shares in lieu of the cash dividend.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
</text>
